       </div>
       <div class="row" style="margin-top: 2%; text-align: center">
         <p>Nothing complex: Just be yourself!</p>
       </div>
       <div class="row" style="margin-top: 2%">
         <div class="col-xs-6" style="text-align: center">
           <div class="modalimg">
